            "title": "Write a Java Program to check Armstrong number.",
            "problem": "Write a Java Program to check Armstrong number.",
            "solution": "public boolean isArmstrong(int number) { \n    int original = number, sum = 0; \n    int digits = String.valueOf(number).length(); \n    while (number > 0) { \n        int digit = number % 10; \n        sum += Math.pow(digit, digits); \n    } \n    return sum == original; \n}",
