            "title": "Write a Java Program to find whether a string or number is",
            "problem": "Write a Java Program to find whether a string or number is",
            "solution": "public boolean isPalindrome(String input) { \n    int left = 0, right = input.length() - 1; \n    while (left < right) { \n        if (input.charAt(left) != input.charAt(right)) { \n            return false; \n        } \n        left++; \n        right--; \n    } \n    return true; \n}",
            "explanation": "This method checks if a string is a palindrome by comparing characters from \nboth ends moving toward the center. If all characters match, it's a palindrome."
